Bot Memo Polish

A simple Java-based application designed to assist with memorization techniques, tailored for Polish language learners.

Features

Flashcard System: Create and review flashcards to enhance vocabulary retention.

Spaced Repetition: Utilize spaced repetition algorithms to optimize review intervals.

Polish Language Support: Specifically designed for Polish language learners.

Prerequisites

Java 8 or higher

Maven for dependency management

Getting Started
Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/ca5ual/bot_memo_polish.git
cd bot_memo_polish

Build the Project
mvn clean install

Run the Application
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="com.example.Main"

Usage

Upon running the application, follow the on-screen prompts to create and review flashcards. The system will guide you through the memorization process using spaced repetition.
